
'''= media coverage on the Occupy movement for internet users not on Twitter and Facebook'''

URL = http://www.supportows.org/about/

=Description=

"Support OWS is designed to bring information from the global Occupy movement, as well as media coverage on the Occupy movement, and join them in such a way that our readers are able to do a side by side comparison of what is being said and what is being done.

As Facebook, Twitter and Youtube are the main sources for actual information from the movement itself, it is difficult for non-FB users and non-Twitter users to gather accurate information about the movement(s), what they stand for, and what they are doing. This site gives every Internet user access to real news as it happens."
(http://www.supportows.org/about/)

